steps.html_instructions:
Turn left onto Epar.Od. Livadochoriou-Karpasio/Epar.Od. Mirina-Moudrou
Continue to follow Epar.Od. Mirina-Moudrou

Posidonos turns left and becomes Ilia Iliou
Go through 2 roundabouts

Take the Kavala - Limnos ferry to Καβάλα
Toll road

Continue straight
Partial restricted usage road
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Erithrou Stavrou/EO2

Turn left to merge onto Egnatia Odos/EO Thessalonikis-Kavalas/A2/E90 toward θεσσαλονίκν/Thessaloniki
Toll road

Take the exit on the left onto A/D Pireos Athinon Thessalonikis Evzonon/Egnatia Odos/A1/A2/E90 toward ATHINA/VEROIA/E75
Toll road

Keep left to continue on A/D Pireos Athinon Thessalonikis Evzonon/NEO Athinon Thessalonikis/A1/E75
Toll road
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto PEO Athinon Thessalonikis/EO1
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Mouson/PEO Athinon Thessalonikis/EO1
At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit onto Par. A/D PATHE heading to ATHINA/LARISA/Route 1

Merge onto A/D Pireos Athinon Thessalonikis Evzonon/NEO Athinon Thessalonikis/A1/E75 via the ramp to LARISSA
Toll road
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto 28is Oktovriou

Continue onto Ευαγ.Κοροβάγγου
Destination will be on the right

summary: Kavala - Limnos and Egnatia Odos/EO Thessalonikis-Kavalas/A2/E90
